Pacquiao has been preparing for his battle with the unbeaten Mayweather in Las Vegas on May 2

According to USA Today Sports, Pacquiao purchased the property on the provision that it came fully furnished and ready to move in. 

Pacquiao has been training at the Wild Card Gym in Los Angeles for his upcoming mega fight against Mayweather in Las Vegas.

And it looks like the 36-year-old has already started to spend some of the money he is expected to earn from the $300million battle at the MGM Grand.

